_sText:
The map is a fun map to play, a terrorist and a counter terrorist will start at 1 end of each huge block and there will be eaither 2 aug's, 2 awp's, 2 sg552's, 2 ak47's or 2 m4a1's this is random everytime. i recomend no more than 8 players otherwise there will be no swapping where you spawn. 
every player starts off with about 92hp as the spawn points are high.
